title: 1 Bedroom Available Soon! Fully Equipped w/Full Size W&D!
map_address: 25900 Chelsea Park Dr near Beech Daly
posting_body: ['<URL>', 'Chelsea Park Apartments is a perfect place to call home!', 'Our spacious apartments afford all of the extra conveniences you are looking for!', "From the in-home washer and dryer to the kitchen with a breakfast bar, you'll be able to settle in quickly with everything you need at your fingertips.", 'Also featured within the kitchen is a complete appliance package (dishwasher, garbage disposal, electric stove, and refrigerator).', 'There are various areas in which to keep belongings organized between the entry, linen, and storage closets.', 'The living room can accommodate larger, sectional furniture sets and just off of it is a generously sized walk-out patio/balcony large enough for a bistro set and potted plants.', 'All this is comfortably maintained by central air conditioning and heat.', 'As a resident of our Community you will enjoy the benefits of:', 'Patio or Balcony', 'Fully Equipped Kitchen Including Dishwasher', 'Full Size Washer & Dryer in Every Home', 'Plenty of Storage w/Walk In Closets', 'Pet-friendly', '24 Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Playground', 'Heated Pool', 'Billiards', 'Fitness Center', 'Tennis Court', 'Ready to reserve now?', 'Great!', 'Start by submitting an application online to us at <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates subject to change without advance notice.', '<URL>']
